TitleEnglish: Doraemon: Nobita in the Wan-Nyan Spacetime Odyssey
SummaryEnglish: An elderly dog goes to a Time travel, which he plans to use to drive to the future so he can meet with "someone" who gives him a kendama. However, the machine encounters "temporal turbulence" and goes haywire and the dog is regressed back to his infant state, eventually found by a researcher cat.
